name: Thul Fain
Lore: 'Gambler who bets on how long the Rancor''s victims will last. Formerly an Imperial pilot who worked with Lieutenant Tanbris. Now a smuggler for Jabba.',
Text: 'Deploys free to your [Independent Starship] starship. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When with Lieutenant Tanbris in a battle at a system, adds 2 to each of your battle destiny draws.',
